---

## Implementation Priorities (Prototype)

1. Basic UI for layer selection  
2. Rule‑based AI Mapping Engine  
3. Routing Orchestrator with simple weighting  
4. Adaptive Memory Engine storing layer counts  
5. Immersive Delivery returning JSON scene configs  
6. Client rendering symbolic scenes per layer  

